data.description: Most wanted property in Malibu Bay. Great for investors or any buyer! Desirable neighborhood in Chapel Trail. 3 bedrooms/2.5 bathrooms. Porcelain Tiles on the main level and wood flooring on the second level and stairs. Large screen patio with just a few steps to the lake. Stainless Steel appliances. Ample storage and parking. Community amenities-clubhouse, tennis court, community pool, and gym. A+ schools and great neighborhood. Easy access to shops, major roads, and entertainment. Move-in ready.
